==================================================
1. BUSINESS CONTEXT
==================================================
This is a car-sharing platform where:
- a renter books a car
- the booking price is based on:
  daily_rate * number_of_days
- discounts may apply if renter satisfies owner-defined rules
  example:
  - if renter has 3+ years experience, apply discount
- deductions or penalties may be added later
  example:
  - damage deduction
  - late return penalty
- a security deposit must be held in escrow
  example:
  - 2500 or 5000 USD equivalent, or localized value in UZS
- the escrow deposit is not the same as the rental payment
- the escrow deposit must be tracked with its own lifecycle
- after successful car return:
  - payment stays captured
  - escrow is released
- in accident/damage cases:
  - all or part of escrow may be deducted
  - escrow may move to disputed/confiscated logic

Important:
- This is a simulation service for a graduation project
- Real bank integration is not required
- Instead, implement realistic statuses, ledger entries, and clean business logic
- Keep design ready for future real payment gateway integration

