11. STATE TRANSITION RULES
==================================================
Implement clear transition policy.

Payment transitions:
- null -> PENDING on creation
- PENDING -> AUTHORIZED
- AUTHORIZED -> CAPTURED
- PENDING -> FAILED
- AUTHORIZED -> FAILED
- PENDING -> CANCELLED
- AUTHORIZED -> CANCELLED
- CAPTURED -> REFUNDED

Escrow transitions:
- null -> HOLD_REQUESTED on creation
- HOLD_REQUESTED -> HELD on authorize
- HELD -> PARTIALLY_RELEASED on partial deduction/release logic
- HELD -> RELEASED
- HELD -> CONFISCATED
- HELD -> DISPUTED
- PARTIALLY_RELEASED -> RELEASED
- PARTIALLY_RELEASED -> CONFISCATED
- PARTIALLY_RELEASED -> DISPUTED

Rejected transitions must throw business exception.

Create:
- PaymentTransitionPolicy
- EscrowTransitionPolicy

